OL,7,FShe has today refused to be drawn into
OL,8,Fthe row over the appointment of its
OL,9,Finterim fire chief Stuart Millington,
OL,10,Fhimself at the centre of bullying
OL,11,Fallegations.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government took over
OL,14,Fresponsibility for South Wales Fire
OL,15,Fand Rescue Service after a damning
OL,16,Freport exposed a toxic culture in the
OL,17,Fservice and the departure of its chief
OL,18,FHuw Jakeway.
