OL,7,FThe Deputy Minister for Social
OL,8,FPartnership told the committee that
OL,9,Fshe first became aware of the
OL,10,Fallegations centring around the
OL,11,Fservice following and she "was not
OL,12,Faware" of the workplace culture issues
OL,13,Fbefore that.
OL,15,FMs Blythyn said: "As soon as that came
OL,16,Fforward (ITV report), I met with the
OL,17,Fchief and the chair of the rescue and
OL,18,Ffire authority in South Wales".
