OL,7,FEarlier this month Hannah Blythyn,
OL,8,Fannounced the appointment of four
OL,9,Fcommissioners to oversee the reform of
OL,10,Fthe service. They included former
OL,11,FMinister for Education, Kirsty
OL,12,FWilliams, and former Chief Constable
OL,13,Fof North Wales Police, Carl Foulkes.
OL,15,FShe told the committee: "The
OL,16,Fcommissioners were chosen on a range
OL,17,Fof experience, balance of that
OL,18,Fexperience, background and skills and
OL,19,Findependence.
