OL,7,F"We wanted to make sure we had a
OL,8,Fmixture of both fire and rescue
OL,9,Fservice operational knowledge but also
OL,10,Fan understanding of the key elements."
OL,12,FWhen questioned over the appointment
OL,13,Fof Stuart Millington, Ms Blythyn
OL,14,Fdefended the decision and said: "The
OL,15,Fcommissioners needed to act to seek an
OL,16,Finterim replacement for an interim
OL,17,Fchief fire officer. That decision was
OL,18,Fmade and then Welsh Government
OL,19,Fofficials were informed."
