OL,7,F"There are very few organisations that
OL,8,Fare going to be immune from these
OL,9,Fchallenges, and I think there really
OL,10,Fis a role for trade union colleagues
OL,11,Fas part of that too.
OL,13,F"I say this as somebody who's worked
OL,14,Fin the trade union movement
OL,15,Fpreviously, sadly those organisations
OL,16,Faren't immune from it either."
