OL,7,FThe deputy minister revealed that she
OL,8,Fwill meet with trade unions this week.
OL,9,FShe said: "Clearly, as part of this,
OL,10,Fthe workforce needs to be part of the
OL,11,Fprocess to achieve that cultural
OL,12,Fchange too and I've referenced the
OL,13,Fterms of reference of the
OL,14,Fcommissioners earlier and that does
OL,15,Fpoint out the need to do this in
OL,16,Fsocial partnership."
OL,18,FShe added: "Clearly, there is an
OL,19,Fendemic societal issue that is
OL,20,Fparticularly affecting male-dominated
OL,21,Fworkplaces.
